# Cursor Repository Entry

Start with `AGENTS.md`.

Then read:

1. `docs/AI_WORKFLOW.md`
2. `docs/DOC_METADATA_SPEC.md`
3. `README.md`
4. Task-relevant docs:
   - `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md`
   - `docs/VISUAL_SYSTEMS.md`
   - `docs/MAINTAINER_WORKFLOW.md`
   - `.cursor/workflows/doc-sync-workflow.md`

Do not maintain a separate Cursor-only workflow here if the same rule already belongs in `AGENTS.md` or `docs/AI_WORKFLOW.md`.
